Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.12,0:00:54.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我要反问一句\N{\fs38}But here's my reverse ask--
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.79,0:00:57.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我[哔]为什么要这么做\N{\fs38}Why in the [bleep] would I ever do that, ever?
