Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.22,0:04:42.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你来了就好 Rick\N{\fs38}Well, it's good you're here, Rick.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.50,0:04:44.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们自己肯定搞不定\N{\fs38}I was pretty sure we didn't have what it takes
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.06,0:04:45.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个吸血的东西的\N{\fs38}to deal with a bloodsucker on our own.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.60,0:04:47.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别妄自菲薄 Summer\N{\fs38}Don't short-sell yourself, Summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.10,0:04:49.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你完全能做到 但是我们[哔]组队的话\N{\fs38}You got everything it takes. But it'll still be fun
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.37,0:04:52.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是很有趣啊 小Rick[哔]无敌\N{\fs38}To do this as a [bleep] team, mother[bleep] tiny Rick!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.85,0:04:54.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天呐 Toby Matthews来了\N{\fs38}Oh, my god, Toby Matthews!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.87,0:04:56.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗨 我是小Rick 我新来的\N{\fs38}Hey, Toby. I'm tiny Rick. I'm new.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.70,0:04:59.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别欺负我哦 哈哈 开玩笑的\N{\fs38}Hey oh-- go easy on me. Ha ha. Just kiddin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.15,0:05:01.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就喜欢你这种直接的性格\N{\fs38}I like your straightforward style.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.80,0:05:03.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这实验服的行头挺酷的\N{\fs38}And that lab coat's pretty cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.07,0:05:04.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好啊Summer\N{\fs38}Summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.56,0:05:06.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他知道我的名字\N{\fs38}He knew my name!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.61,0:05:08.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他怎么会不知道 你长这么美\N{\fs38}Why wouldn't he? You're great!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.24,0:05:09.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我们还是小心为妙\N{\fs38}But, listen, just be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.60,0:05:11.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们不能排除任何人是吸血鬼的嫌疑\N{\fs38}We can't rule anybody out as the vampire,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.55,0:05:13.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,男神也不行\N{\fs38}Not even the dreamboats.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.49,0:05:14.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讨厌\N{\fs38}Stop, tiny Rick.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.76,0:05:16.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟孙子孙女杀吸血鬼去啦\N{\fs38}Huntin' a vampire with my grandkids!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.00,0:05:18.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小Rick[哔]无敌\N{\fs38}[bleep]tiny Rick!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.77,0:05:21.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下一步是观察你们的构造体\N{\fs38}The next step is to watch your mythologues
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.75,0:05:24.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,观察他们之间的互动 "意外"的是\N{\fs38}interact together and, uh-- big surprise--
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.65,0:05:25.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,场面从来都不好看\N{\fs38}It's never pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.98,0:05:29.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是Gloompfschs夫妇\N{\fs38}Here we have Garrrh and Zharbidar Gloompfschs,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.48,0:05:31.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,换种说法\N{\fs38}Or, should I say, here we have the way
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.58,0:05:34.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是这对夫妇对对方的感知\N{\fs38}Garrrh and Zharbidar perceive each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.57,0:05:37.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很明显\N{\fs38}As we can all see,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.75,0:05:39.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这根本不是他们本来的样子\N{\fs38}This is hardly the real Garrrh and Zharbidar.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.90,0:05:41.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过这很好 因为在他们脑海里\N{\fs38}Which is good, because the relationship
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.80,0:05:43.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们的婚姻关系不仅丑恶\N{\fs38}In their heads is not only ugly,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.21,0:05:45.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且难以维系\N{\fs38}It's unsustainable.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.59,0:05:52.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们可能已经学到了重要的一课\N{\fs38}You may already be learning something important--
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.69,0:05:54.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们看到的所有婚姻关系都各不相同\N{\fs38}All of these relationships are different,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.97,0:05:57.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都不真实 而且没有一对能行的通\N{\fs38}None of them are real, and none of them work.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.01,0:06:01.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们并不是对方时常认为的魔鬼模样\N{\fs38}We are not the monsters we sometimes see each other as,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.43,0:06:05.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我们是真实的 我们是协调的\N{\fs38}Because we are real and we are functional.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.64,0:06:08.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正因为此 我们比这些怪物好多了\N{\fs38}That's what makes us better than them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.93,0:06:10.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们能解决问题\N{\fs38}We can find solutions.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.17,0:06:12.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能相互适应\N{\fs38}We can adapt.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.83,0:06:14.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能相互交流\N{\fs38}We can communicate.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.14,0:06:17.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最重要的是\N{\fs38}And, most importantly,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.19,0:06:22.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们能相互合作\N{\fs38}We can work together.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.09,0:06:26.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然颇有坎坷 最后终于苦尽甘来\N{\fs38}Well, it was a tough adventure, but it paid off --
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.45,0:06:28.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学校里没有吸血鬼啦\N{\fs38}Our school is vampire-free!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.42,0:06:30.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到Feratu教练竟然是吸血鬼\N{\fs38}Man, who would've suspected coach Feratu?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.42,0:06:30.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs38\an8}这个名字出自著名的吸血鬼诺斯费拉图
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.00,0:06:32.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们做得很好 功不可没\N{\fs38}You did great, guys. Couldn't have done it without ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.93,0:06:34.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们要为自己感到骄傲\N{\fs38}You know, we-- w-we should be proud of ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.86,0:06:37.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们杀了一个吸血鬼 同时干掉一个体育老师\N{\fs38}We killed a vampire and a gym teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.07,0:06:39.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈哈 也算一石二鸟\N{\fs38}Ha ha ha. Talk about two-for-one, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.22,0:06:41.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你原本的身体是\N{\fs38}So, how, exactly, is your old body
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.14,0:06:42.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么在这里面维持生命的啊\N{\fs38}living in there, grandpa Rick?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.61,0:06:44.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是高压氧量子液体\N{\fs38}Oh, you know, hyperbaric quantum fluid,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.55,0:06:45.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乱七八糟的东西\N{\fs38}That kind of thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.67,0:06:47.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以保存生物组织\N{\fs38}It preserves living tissue.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.10,0:06:48.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也没多少东西要保存的了\N{\fs38}Not that there was much to preserve.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.53,0:06:50.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看那皮包骨跟木乃伊似的\N{\fs38}Look at that mummy! Ha! Ha ha!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.65,0:06:53.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我该回到那老家伙的身体里了\N{\fs38}And I guess it's time for me to get back inside the old-timer.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.61,0:06:57.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天呐Toby Matthews问我父母在不在家\N{\fs38}Oh, my god. Toby Matthews is asking if my parents
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.43,0:06:59.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还问我能不能开派对\N{\fs38}Are still out of town and if we can have a party!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.18,0:07:01.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真棒 Summer 你看我上午说什么来着\N{\fs38}All right, way to go, Summer! What did I tell you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.85,0:07:04.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他还问小Rick会不会来\N{\fs38}Ohh! He's asking if tiny Rick will be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.91,0:07:06.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Summer 我转念一想\N{\fs38}Well, you know what, Summer?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.13,0:07:08.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你告诉他 小Rick会过去的\N{\fs38}Tell him tiny Rick will be here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.19,0:07:09.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让他带点酒来\N{\fs38}And tell him to bring some brews!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.75,0:07:12.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗 你 你会以小Rick的身份留下\N{\fs38}For real? Y-y-y-you would stay as tiny Rick,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.47,0:07:12.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就为了留下来开派对\N{\fs38}Just so we can have a party?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.67,0:07:15.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 多一晚又有什么关系\N{\fs38}Hell, yeah! What's one more night?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.71,0:07:18.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再说这老家伙在这儿 谁能尽兴啊\N{\fs38}And who can have fun with this old bastard hanging around, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.07,0:07:20.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Wubby lubby doob doob\N{\fs38}Wubby lubby doob doob!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.35,0:07:22.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小Rick\N{\fs38}Tiny Rick!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.51,0:07:27.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来 这边是Beth和Jerry Smith\N{\fs38}Moving on. Now, we have beth and jerry smith
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.81,0:07:29.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来自地一球行星\N{\fs38}From the planet e-arth.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.51,0:07:30.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的心跳得很厉害\N{\fs38}My heart is pounding.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.52,0:07:31.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定会很棒\N{\fs38}This is gonna be great.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.53,0:07:33.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,地一球的两性关系比较简单\N{\fs38}The e-arth relationships are simpler.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.61,0:07:36.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它是一个原始星球 所以他们的失调状态\N{\fs38}It's a primitive planet, so their dysfunctions are oh --
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.27,0:07:38.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 发生了什么\N{\fs38}W-wait, what? What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.33,0:07:39.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Smith夫妇的构造体在哪\N{\fs38}Where are the smith mythologues?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.97,0:07:45.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的天啊\N{\fs38}Oh, my god.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.49,0:07:51.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 天啊  - 守住那个牢房\N{\fs38}- Oh, my god. - Secure the cell!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.25,0:07:56.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁想参观一下礼品店 很有趣的\N{\fs38}Uh, hey! You know what's fun? Our gift shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.71,0:07:58.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们何不有序地前往\N{\fs38}Why don't we proceed in an orderly --
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.55,0:08:02.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的老天\N{\fs38}Oh, dear god, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.75,0:08:04.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们是互利共生的\N{\fs38}They're codependent!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.62,0:08:05.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快跑\N{\fs38}Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.73,0:08:16.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的 你真的很会驾驭\N{\fs38}Oh, yeah, yeah, you really know how to
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.89,0:08:18.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 蓝色的衣服啊  - 真的吗\N{\fs38}- sport that color blue. - Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.65,0:08:20.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 你今天真的很美  - 我的天啊 \N{\fs38}- You're looking real good. - Oh, my god.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.65,0:08:23.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 你好 Morty  - 你好啊 Jessica\N{\fs38}- Hey, morty. Oh, hey - hey, Jessica.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.23,0:08:26.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 小Rick是你的亲兄弟还是表的\N{\fs38}So, is tiny Rick your brother or cousin, or...?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.88,0:08:28.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都不是 我外公把他的意识\N{\fs38}No, my grandpa just transferred
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.43,0:08:30.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,转移到他自己的克隆体上了\N{\fs38}His consciousness into a clone of himself
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.15,0:08:31.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样他就可以来我们学校了\N{\fs38}So he could be in our high school.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.49,0:08:32.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帅气\N{\fs38}Cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.25,0:08:34.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快来看 小Rick在弹吉他\N{\fs38}Hey, tiny Rick's playing guitar.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.65,0:08:35.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各位朋友\N{\fs38}All right, everybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.75,0:08:37.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下一首来自我的内心\N{\fs38}This next one's coming straight from the heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.37,0:08:39.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想到哪儿唱到哪儿 现场发挥的歌词\N{\fs38}Making the lyrics up right off the top of my head.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.01,0:08:42.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,*放我出来 你所见的*\N{\fs38}*Let me out, What you see*
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.29,0:08:44.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,*只是一个假的驱壳*\N{\fs38}*is not the  same person as me*
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.37,0:08:47.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,*我的生活是个谎言 我不是你望着的那个人*\N{\fs38}*My life's a lie, I'm not who you're looking at*
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.35,0:08:50.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,*放我出来 给我自由 我已年迈*\N{\fs38}*Let me out, set me free,I'm really old *
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.21,0:08:51.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,*这不是真正的我*\N{\fs38}*This isn't me*
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.27,0:08:54.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,*我的身体在大缸里渐渐死亡*\N{\fs38}*My real body's slowly dying in a vat*
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.42,0:09:00.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,*有人听到我的呐喊吗 有人明白我吗*\N{\fs38}*Is anybody listening, can anyone understand*
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.51,0:09:03.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,*别再傻盯着我了 救救我吧*\N{\fs38}*Stop Looking at me like that and actually help me*
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.97,0:09:06.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,*救我 救救我 我要死了*\N{\fs38}*Help! Help me, I'm gonna die*
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.07,0:09:08.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是小Rick 谢谢捧场\N{\fs38}Tiny Rick! Thanks, everybody!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.67,0:09:09.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙太赞了\N{\fs38}This guy's amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.92,0:09:11.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 我爱小Rick   - 帅飞了\N{\fs38}- I love tiny Rick! - Bad ass.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.04,0:09:35.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搞什么[哔]\N{\fs38}What the [bleep]?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.45,0:09:37.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是 你们这机构怎么搞的\N{\fs38}Yeah, I know! What kind of operation are you running?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.01,0:09:40.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们 你们两夫妇是什么的婚姻关系啊\N{\fs38}Us?! What the hell kind of relationship do you have?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.91,0:09:42.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真好 怪在我们的头上\N{\fs38}Oh, right, blame this on us.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.27,0:09:45.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对 没错 我就怪在你们头上\N{\fs38}Okay, uh, I can and I am!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.47,0:09:48.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们的恶魔化构造体居然在合作\N{\fs38}Your demonized mythologizations of each other are cooperating.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.89,0:09:50.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是好事吗\N{\fs38}Isn't that good?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.13,0:09:52.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才不是 糟透了\N{\fs38}No. No! It's bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.53,0:09:55.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们的婚姻是我见过最糟的\N{\fs38}You have the single worst marriage I've ever witnessed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.83,0:09:56.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根本不应该存在\N{\fs38}It shouldn't exist!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.87,0:09:59.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们根本完全彻底不应该在一起\N{\fs38}You should never, ever, ever, have gotten together
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.63,0:10:01.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还很不懂你们是怎么以及为什么\N{\fs38}And I do not understand how, or why,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.05,0:10:04.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会走到一起\N{\fs38}You would ever stay together.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.65,0:10:07.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这婚姻咨询也太烂了吧\N{\fs38}Well, this is just bad couples' therapy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.25,0:10:08.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可不是嘛\N{\fs38}Totally.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.57,0:10:19.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等我们\N{\fs38}Wait for us!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.31,0:10:20.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,位置只够再多一人了\N{\fs38}There's only room for one more.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.85,0:10:22.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是心理咨询师 我跟他们说说\N{\fs38}I'm a therapist. I'll talk to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.59,0:10:24.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们不是咨询师 马上走\N{\fs38}They're not therapists. Go, go, go!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.69,0:10:27.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定有办法联系上爸爸的\N{\fs38}There's gotta be a way to contact my dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.39,0:10:29.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们找个控制室什么的\N{\fs38}Let's find a control room or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.21,0:10:36.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Beth 快来看看\N{\fs38}Beth! You'll want to see this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.91,0:10:37.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么\N{\fs38}What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.67,0:10:39.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是个小型可拆卸面板\N{\fs38}It's a small, hinged panel
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.27,0:10:42.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,后面有一些空间\N{\fs38}With a tiny amount of space behind it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.77,0:10:43.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你也能找到一个\N{\fs38}If you can find one, too,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.01,0:10:46.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来几个小时或几天我们就安全了\N{\fs38}We should be safe for hours, maybe days!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.57,0:10:49.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Jerry 你在这里待好\N{\fs38}You stay put, Jerry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.79,0:10:51.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去求救 假如我能活着的话\N{\fs38}I'll send help, if I make it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.29,0:10:53.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不找个地方自己躲起来吗\N{\fs38}You don't want to find your own little hatch?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.75,0:10:56.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Jerry 我相信你独自躲好的话\N{\fs38}Jerry, I believe that, if you hide by yourself,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.81,0:10:58.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可以活下去\N{\fs38}You might survive and I believe I,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.97,0:11:01.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同时我也相信 我独自也能逃出这里\N{\fs38}By myself, have a shot of getting out of here,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.33,0:11:03.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我们两人一起\N{\fs38}But the two of us, together?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.21,0:11:05.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道\N{\fs38}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.61,0:11:07.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能那个心理医生是对的\N{\fs38}Look, maybe the shrink was right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.93,0:11:09.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祝你好运\N{\fs38}Good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.47,0:11:13.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你给我听好了\N{\fs38}All right, now, you listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.87,0:11:15.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实不听也可以\N{\fs38}Oh! Or don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.09,0:11:17.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别 求你了\N{\fs38}Hey! Don't! Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.95,0:11:21.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天啊 别过来\N{\fs38}Oh, god, oh, god, oh, god!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.79,0:11:23.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白我以前说过什么\N{\fs38}Now, I know I've said, in the past,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.43,0:11:25.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,数学很重要 确实是\N{\fs38}That math is important -- and it is! --
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.47,0:11:28.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还认为 总有一天 你们会回想起\N{\fs38}But I also think that, one day, you'll all look back
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.09,0:11:31.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟小Rick和Morty做同学的日子\N{\fs38}On being in high school with tiny Rick and Morty,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.66,0:11:34.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为听说他们昨晚搞了一个超级棒的派对\N{\fs38}Who I hear had a great party last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.61,0:11:36.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 下课\N{\fs38}So, class dismissed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.63,0:11:37.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天放你们假\N{\fs38}You've got the day off!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.87,0:11:40.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干的好 Goldenfold先生\N{\fs38}All right! Good work, mr. Goldenfold!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.04,0:11:42.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错 到外面转转 多读书\N{\fs38}Yeah, get outside. Read a book.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.11,0:11:43.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Danielle 涂点防晒霜\N{\fs38}Put on some sunscreen, Danielle!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.67,0:11:45.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Summer 你好 上衣真漂亮\N{\fs38}Hey, what's up, Summer? Ooh, nice top.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.67,0:11:47.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你 小Rick 你觉得\N{\fs38}Thanks. Tiny rick, you think you might be
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.49,0:11:49.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你今晚可以回到老的身体里去吗\N{\fs38}Getting back into your old body tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.21,0:11:51.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行喔 今晚是舞会之夜\N{\fs38}No can do. Tonight's the big dance
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.28,0:11:53.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Morty还会带Jessica出席 他需要这架小僚机\N{\fs38}And Morty's bringing Jessica. He needs his tiny wing man.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.79,0:11:55.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小Rick\N{\fs38}Tiny Rick!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.57,0:11:58.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今晚不行的话要等到什么时候\N{\fs38}Okay, but if not tonight, when?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.11,0:11:59.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不清楚 等我想回去了\N{\fs38}I don't know. When I feel like it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.79,0:12:02.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你别这么咄咄逼人的\N{\fs38}Damn, girl! You need to chill out!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.06,0:12:04.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这件事是你先想出来的\N{\fs38}This whole thing was your idea, in the first place,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.06,0:12:05.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在又是你想尽快结束\N{\fs38}And, now, you're trying to rush it along.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.85,0:12:07.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可不是嘛 我喜欢高中\N{\fs38}Yeah, and you know what? I like high school.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.37,0:12:09.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我喜欢跟大家玩 小Rick万岁\N{\fs38}I like hanging out. Tiny rick!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.10,0:12:12.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是如果喜欢这样生活的人不是真正的你呢\N{\fs38}But what if the you that likes it isn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.47,0:12:15.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别傻了 Summer\N{\fs38}Oh, Summer!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.91,0:12:17.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是有个年轻驱壳的Rick\N{\fs38}It's just Rick in a younger body.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.37,0:12:18.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会 会 会 会\N{\fs38}What's the -- what's -- what's -- what's --
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.61,0:12:19.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会有什么问题啊\N{\fs38}What's the -- what's the problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.15,0:12:21.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看看他的画 Morty\N{\fs38}Look at his art, Morty.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.83,0:12:23.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我最近走情绪摇滚风\N{\fs38}I've got an emo streak.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.17,0:12:24.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也算是我这么酷炫的部分原因\N{\fs38}It's part of what makes me so rad.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.48,0:12:27.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么这里写着"救救我 Morty和Summer"\N{\fs38}Why does it say "Help me morty and summer!"?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.73,0:12:29.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Summer 这是画的题目\N{\fs38}Come on, Summer, that's the title of the art.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.93,0:12:31.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么<霹雳游侠>叫霹雳游侠\N{\fs38}Why was knight rider called knight rider?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.93,0:12:31.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs38\an8}<霹雳游侠> 80年代电视剧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.67,0:12:34.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,车的名字明明是Kitt 被人开的不是Michael Knight.\N{\fs38}The car's name was kitt. Nobody rode Michael Knight.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.67,0:12:34.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs38\an8}男主名叫Michael Knight
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.17,0:12:36.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想多了 Summer 我是小Rick\N{\fs38}You're overthinking it, summer. I'm tiny rick!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.67,0:12:38.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,外公 我觉得 你把意识\N{\fs38}Grandpa, I think that, when you put your mind
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.09,0:12:40.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放进这个年轻的躯体了\N{\fs38}Into this body's young brain,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.47,0:12:41.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他就做年轻人做的事\N{\fs38}It did what young brains do --
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.93,0:12:43.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这副躯体把坏的想法压在心底\N{\fs38}It shoved the bad thoughts into the back
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.07,0:12:45.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,掩藏起来\N{\fs38}And put a wall around them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.79,0:12:48.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但那些想法属于真正的Rick\N{\fs38}But those bad thoughts are the real Rick.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.29,0:12:50.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你已经年迈的事实\N{\fs38}The fact that you're old, the fact that
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.05,0:12:51.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们终有一天会死的事实\N{\fs38}We're all going to die, one day, the fact that
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.71,0:12:53.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宇宙很大 任何事都很渺小的事实\N{\fs38}The universe is so big, nothing in it matters,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.99,0:12:55.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些事实才造就真正的你\N{\fs38}Those facts are who you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.87,0:12:57.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以真正的Rick被困住了\N{\fs38}So you're trapped in there and you can only
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.63,0:13:00.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你只能通过小Rick的青少年焦虑表现出来\N{\fs38}Come out in the form of tiny rick's teen angst!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.11,0:13:02.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Summer 我听说\N{\fs38}Well, Summer, I hear
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.89,0:13:05.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Toby Matthews 不喜欢神经兮兮瞎分析的女孩\N{\fs38}Toby Matthews isn't into psycho chicks.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.45,0:13:06.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有人喜欢这类女孩\N{\fs38}Can't think of anyone that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.05,0:13:09.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舞会上见啦 兔崽子们 小Rick万岁\N{\fs38}I'll see you mother at the dance! Tiny rick!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.71,0:13:11.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Morty 你要帮我\N{\fs38}Morty, you have to help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.23,0:13:13.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Summer 他很开心 我也很开心 \N{\fs38}Summer, he's happy! I'm happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.61,0:13:15.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是你的目的吗\N{\fs38}I-I-is that why you're doing this,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.23,0:13:16.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不让我们开心\N{\fs38}You don't want me and rick to be happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.75,0:13:17.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是\N{\fs38}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.57,0:13:18.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就把你这些逼事儿收拾收拾\N{\fs38}Well, then get your shit together!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.05,0:13:21.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全收起来放到书包里\N{\fs38}Get it all together and put it in a backpack.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.69,0:13:24.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有的逼事儿 好好收拾收拾\N{\fs38}All your shit, so it's together.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.27,0:13:26.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你想把它们带走\N{\fs38}And if you gotta take it somewhere,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.81,0:13:28.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就快带走 懂吗\N{\fs38}Take it somewhere, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.09,0:13:29.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,带到逼事儿店卖了\N{\fs38}Take it to the shit store and sell it
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.63,0:13:32.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或者在逼事儿博物馆展览 我不管\N{\fs38}O-or put it in a shit museum. I don't care what you do!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.17,0:13:33.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之 收拾好你的破逼事儿\N{\fs38}You just gotta get it together.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.00,0:13:36.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,收拾好\N{\fs38}Get your shit together.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.13,0:13:44.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别过来\N{\fs38}Get back!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.07,0:13:46.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 不是吧\N{\fs38}Wait, for real?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.77,0:13:49.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是Beth对我的看法\N{\fs38}You're how Beth sees me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.99,0:13:51.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天啊\N{\fs38}Oh, my god.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.05,0:13:53.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,转过身去\N{\fs38}Turn around!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.33,0:13:54.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说转过身去\N{\fs38}I said turn around!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.89,0:13:57.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Beth怎么会这样想我\N{\fs38}How can beth have these thoughts about me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.35,0:13:59.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个狗眼看人低的贱人\N{\fs38}That judgmental monster bitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.05,0:14:01.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可不接受\N{\fs38}I'm not taking this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.28,0:14:02.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想知道我的妻子在哪\N{\fs38}I want to know where my wife is.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.77,0:14:04.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要协助我\N{\fs38}You are going to help me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.17,0:14:07.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,停 别再这样了\N{\fs38}No! Nobody's doing that!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.13,0:14:12.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别动\N{\fs38}Stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.25,0:14:13.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想干嘛\N{\fs38}What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.25,0:14:14.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,更多Jerry\N{\fs38}Jerrys.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.57,0:14:16.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想要Jerry\N{\fs38}You want jerry?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.59,0:14:18.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我都不想要Jerry\N{\fs38}I don't even want jerry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.09,0:14:21.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要很多Jerry\N{\fs38}I want Jerrys.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.21,0:14:23.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一支Jerry军队\N{\fs38}An army.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.83,0:14:26.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Jerry军队\N{\fs38}An army of jerrys.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.45,0:14:30.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他的顺从的价值都浪费在你身上了\N{\fs38}The value of his subservience is wasted on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.07,0:14:33.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要利用它来征服宇宙\N{\fs38}I will use it to dominate the universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.37,0:14:34.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天啊 Jerry肯定觉得\N{\fs38}Ah ha ha. Boy, Jerry must think
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.81,0:14:36.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我得多愚蠢 你才会这么蠢\N{\fs38}I'm pretty stupid, for you to be this stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.13,0:14:39.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你把我那个笨蛋丈夫放在\N{\fs38}Wouldn't it make more sense to put my dumbass husband
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.49,0:14:40.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这椅子上不更合理吗\N{\fs38}In this chair, so you can make
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.65,0:14:42.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就可以制造一堆厉害的自己了\N{\fs38}An army of your bad-ass self?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.85,0:14:46.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我永远独一无二\N{\fs38}There could never be more than one of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.32,0:14:48.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是世上最强最聪明的生物\N{\fs38}I'm the strongest, smartest being alive
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.82,0:14:52.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为那就是Jerry所认为的你\N{\fs38}Because jerry thinks you're that much stronger
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.28,0:14:55.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比你要聪明和强大的程度\N{\fs38}And smarter than you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.93,0:14:57.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧 嗷\N{\fs38}Okay, ouch.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.93,0:15:06.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Morty Jessica 干嘛呢\N{\fs38}Morty, Jessica, what's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.29,0:15:07.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快来欣赏一下的我的自创舞蹈\N{\fs38}Check out the new dance I made up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.83,0:15:09.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叫做"啊 放我出去"\N{\fs38}It's called "Ooh let me out!"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.09,0:15:13.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,*放我出来 放我出来 我不是在跳舞*\N{\fs38}*Let me out. Let me out. This is not a dance.*
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.15,0:15:16.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,*我乞求帮助 我需要帮助*\N{\fs38}*I'm begging for help, I'm screaming for help*
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.29,0:15:17.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,*请放我出来吧*\N{\fs38}*Please come let me out*
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.97,0:15:21.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,*放我出来 放我出来 我不是在跳舞*\N{\fs38}*Let me out, let me out, this is not a dance*
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.07,0:15:24.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,*我乞求帮助 我需要帮助*\N{\fs38}*I'M I'm beging for help, I'm screaming for help*
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.31,0:15:25.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,*请放我出来*\N{\fs38}*Please come let me out*
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.69,0:15:28.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,*我在一个车库的大缸中正在死去*\N{\fs38}*I'm dying in a vat in a garage*
